1
00:00:00,720 --> 00:00:02,850
Previously on Fairy Tail:

2
00:00:02,850 --> 00:00:05,940
Nirvana was fired toward Caitshelter,

3
00:00:05,940 --> 00:00:10,570
but thanks to the magic bombs 
from Christina, it barely missed!

4
00:00:10,570 --> 00:00:14,160
The Tri-mens, Lyon, and Sherry 
managed to make Christina fly

5
00:00:14,160 --> 00:00:16,700
with what little magic power they had left,

6
00:00:16,700 --> 00:00:18,670
but Christina is crashing!

7
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:54,450
Nirvana has been sealed since long, long ago.

8
00:01:54,450 --> 00:01:58,880
It is an ultra-inversion magic 
which replaces darkness and light.

9
00:01:58,880 --> 00:02:02,350
The seal was broken deep 
inside the Worth Woodsea

10
00:02:02,350 --> 00:02:07,480
by the Dark Guild, Oracion Seis, who 
wished to gain Nirvana for themselves.

11
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:12,860
In order to prevent that, an alliance 
of official guilds was formed.

12
00:02:12,860 --> 00:02:17,490
From Fairy Tail: Natsu, Lucy, Gray, and Erza.

13
00:02:17,490 --> 00:02:22,200
From Blue Pegasus: Hibiki, 
Ren, Eve, and Ichiya.

14
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:26,030
From Lamia Scale: Lyon, Sherry, and Jura.

15
00:02:26,030 --> 00:02:30,460
And from Caitshelter, 
Wendy also participated.

16
00:02:30,700 --> 00:02:37,040
Plus Jellal, who should have sunk into the sea together with the Tower of Heaven,

17
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:38,670
also joined the fray.

18
00:02:39,550 --> 00:02:43,370
After many fierce battles, Oracion 
Seis was finally defeated,

19
00:02:43,370 --> 00:02:49,520
but with the appearance of Master Zero, Natsu 
and the others are facing their greatest crisis!

20
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,350
One!

21
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:52,550
Two!

22
00:02:52,550 --> 00:02:53,800
I'll go to three!

23
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,840
I just hope Zero's not there!

24
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,630
I will head to four.

25
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:01,200
My parfum tells me that it 
is the closest one to me.

26
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:03,620
The map is what told you.

27
00:03:03,620 --> 00:03:06,520
Was it really necessary to correct me?

28
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,080
I'll take five.

29
00:03:08,330 --> 00:03:09,830
You're six.

30
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:14,280
The Power of Feelings!

31
00:03:30,790 --> 00:03:33,440
Damn, this tunnel is long.

32
00:03:36,950 --> 00:03:41,950
Finally, I'm here... Lacrima number two.

33
00:03:42,650 --> 00:03:45,580
So I gotta destroy this thing, then.

34
00:03:50,850 --> 00:03:55,180
Doesn't look like Master Zero's here.

35
00:03:56,550 --> 00:04:01,100
So that means someone else has to fight him.

36
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:06,160
This is lacrima number one.

37
00:04:21,700 --> 00:04:23,360
Jellal...

38
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:30,450
I see... So, your memories have returned?

39
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,500
Yeah.

40
00:04:40,550 --> 00:04:42,050
You bastard...

41
00:04:46,510 --> 00:04:48,890
Jellal!

42
00:04:49,890 --> 00:04:50,720
Natsu...

43
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:58,150
Fire ain't gonna work on me!

44
00:04:58,150 --> 00:05:01,230
I know. I remember.

45
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:05,490
You're Natsu... Our only hope.

46
00:05:05,490 --> 00:05:06,780
What?!

47
00:05:06,780 --> 00:05:07,860
Huh?

48
00:05:08,570 --> 00:05:14,870
The Fire Dragon Slayer. Your magic power 
increases from the power of flames.

49
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,950
Power of flames?

50
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:24,300
You... Doesn't seem like your memories 
have totally returned at all.

51
00:05:24,710 --> 00:05:28,220
It's as I said... I remembered 
Natsu, that is all.

52
00:05:28,750 --> 00:05:30,630
I will stop Nirvana.

53
00:05:31,020 --> 00:05:35,170
What I am trying to do has not changed, Zero.

54
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:38,150
What do you mean, memories?

55
00:05:38,450 --> 00:05:42,460
I do not have any memories prior 
to waking up in this land.

56
00:05:43,390 --> 00:05:46,340
I know I was the worst kind of human trash...

57
00:05:46,700 --> 00:05:48,230
But I'm not aware of it myself.

58
00:05:48,650 --> 00:05:52,050
All I know is it seems I caused 
you and Erza some great injury...

59
00:05:52,660 --> 00:05:56,000
But now, I wish to protect Wendy's guild.

60
00:05:56,340 --> 00:05:57,920
I wish to stop Nirvana.

61
00:05:58,500 --> 00:06:00,960
I wish to be of help to all of you!

62
00:06:01,540 --> 00:06:03,600
Like hell you do!

63
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:06,040
Are you sayin' you forgot all that?

64
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:08,790
You can't get away with 
pretending to be my ally!

65
00:06:08,790 --> 00:06:12,550
Please, Natsu... Accept this flame!

66
00:06:14,340 --> 00:06:16,310
Well, I didn't forget.

67
00:06:16,650 --> 00:06:18,410
I'll never forget Erza's tears!

68
00:06:18,990 --> 00:06:21,980
You... You...

69
00:06:21,980 --> 00:06:24,730
You made Erza cry!

70
00:06:26,690 --> 00:06:31,530
Sheesh... If you're going to squabble 
amongst yourselves, can you please do it elsewhere?

71
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:34,160
It's annoying!

72
00:06:58,190 --> 00:06:59,250
You...

73
00:07:04,860 --> 00:07:07,630
If you want to do me in, 
you can do it anytime.

74
00:07:08,010 --> 00:07:10,860
I'm already on my last legs...

75
00:07:11,350 --> 00:07:14,970
Now... The power to defeat that guy...

76
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:21,180
Golden flames...

77
00:07:22,700 --> 00:07:27,320
And this is the passage to the third lacrima.

78
00:07:29,580 --> 00:07:31,960
You should rest a little, Lucy...

79
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:34,620
No! I won't make it then...

80
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:38,950
But... You can barely walk.

81
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:40,230
Are you okay?

82
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:44,820
What are you talking about? 
I can walk just fine...

83
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:51,090
But... Even if I'm not so okay...

84
00:07:51,350 --> 00:07:54,370
I can't go saying that now!

85
00:07:55,910 --> 00:07:58,830
Men, men, men...

86
00:07:58,830 --> 00:08:02,110
The passage to the fourth lacrima...

87
00:08:02,110 --> 00:08:05,620
I must hurry, no matter what 
happens to this body of mine!

88
00:08:06,790 --> 00:08:09,990
I am Ichiya, of Blue Pegasus!

89
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:14,090
I will fulfill my duty to the end!

90
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:17,190
The fifth lacrima.

91
00:08:17,510 --> 00:08:19,300
Master Zero is not here.

92
00:08:20,460 --> 00:08:23,690
As I thought, he's at lacrima number 
one, which Natsu headed towards.

93
00:08:25,730 --> 00:08:26,790
Natsu...

94
00:08:33,030 --> 00:08:35,860
This is the flame of guilt.

95
00:08:38,620 --> 00:08:41,530
The passage to the sixth lacrima...

96
00:08:46,410 --> 00:08:48,290
Thank you, Carla...

97
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:51,250
I hope Jellal is okay...

98
00:08:51,250 --> 00:08:54,040
Don't worry about others, 
worry about yourself!

99
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:56,260
Can you really do this, Wendy?

100
00:08:56,580 --> 00:09:00,770
Yeah! This is something I have to do!

101
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:10,190
Jellal, do you feel okay?

102
00:09:10,190 --> 00:09:14,780
You can use Healing Magic, yes?

103
00:09:15,300 --> 00:09:19,780
Can you recover Natsu's magic 
power during his fight with Natsu?

104
00:09:20,470 --> 00:09:21,740
Well, I...

105
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:27,940
What's this crazy talk? Do you have any idea how 
many times she's used Healing Magic today already?

106
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:30,100
Any more is impossible! You 
know that she's actually...

107
00:09:30,100 --> 00:09:30,910
I see.

108
00:09:32,420 --> 00:09:36,050
Then, I will handle Natsu's recovery.

109
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:44,720
I remember the unfathomable power 
he has... The power of hope.

110
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:51,480
You go destroy the sixth lacrima in my stead.

111
00:09:52,220 --> 00:09:53,810
But I...

112
00:09:54,850 --> 00:09:56,310
I know you can do it.

113
00:09:56,650 --> 00:10:02,450
Dragon Slayer magic was designed to be an 
overwhelming offensive magic for battling dragons.

114
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:05,610
Air...

115
00:10:06,220 --> 00:10:07,880
Or rather, the sky...

116
00:10:08,470 --> 00:10:09,570
Eat the heavens themselves.

117
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:12,690
The power of a dragon sleeps within you.

118
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,200
The heavens?

119
00:10:29,940 --> 00:10:34,230
The power of a dragon... is within me...

120
00:10:34,540 --> 00:10:37,070
This is to protect my guild!

121
00:10:37,070 --> 00:10:40,150
Please, Grandine! Lend me the power!

122
00:10:43,450 --> 00:10:44,720
Wendy...

123
00:10:49,540 --> 00:10:51,190
The flame of guilt?

124
00:10:52,710 --> 00:10:54,520
I don't need you to forgive me...

125
00:10:54,980 --> 00:10:57,580
I just want you to receive this power...

126
00:10:59,110 --> 00:11:01,550
I believe in you.

127
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:09,980
I believe in the man... 
that Erza believes in...

128
00:11:44,390 --> 00:11:46,040
I'm counting on you.

129
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,730
Thanks for the meal.

130
00:11:56,580 --> 00:11:59,650
Don't worry, I've gotten your power, Jellal.

131
00:12:02,470 --> 00:12:04,560
The flame of guilt?

132
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:09,160
By eating that, you take on the same sin...

133
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:11,670
I'm used to that.

134
00:12:11,670 --> 00:12:14,510
For a Fairy Tail wizard,

135
00:12:14,510 --> 00:12:17,790
the true sin is averting one's eyes,

136
00:12:18,250 --> 00:12:23,710
and no longer being able 
to believe in anyone!

137
00:12:47,210 --> 00:12:48,820
This power...

138
00:12:50,500 --> 00:12:52,070
T-That light...

139
00:12:56,990 --> 00:12:59,000
Dragon Force!

140
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:06,670
This lacrima isn't just 
big, it's also damn hard!

141
00:13:08,390 --> 00:13:10,810
I can sense a ton of magic power!

142
00:13:10,810 --> 00:13:12,930
The lacrima is near.

143
00:13:14,570 --> 00:13:16,890
This parfum reeks of danger.

144
00:13:17,530 --> 00:13:19,560
I am close. Men.

145
00:13:21,150 --> 00:13:22,680
The time is near.

146
00:13:23,770 --> 00:13:26,080
Natsu, I believe in you.

147
00:13:28,490 --> 00:13:30,530
Wendy, concentrate!

148
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:33,060
Yeah. I know.

149
00:13:37,040 --> 00:13:38,000
Natsu-san...

150
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:12,350
This power is similar to 
when I ate Etherion...

151
00:14:14,900 --> 00:14:20,460
Whoa... It's like my power's 
doubled, or even tripled...

152
00:14:27,390 --> 00:14:29,130
Dragon Force.

153
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:32,700
The final form of Dragon Slayer Magic.

154
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:39,140
Its magic power is said to rival that of a 
dragon's, capable of annihilating anything.

155
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:42,310
Annihilation!

156
00:14:43,210 --> 00:14:44,680
Interesting!

157
00:14:46,760 --> 00:14:48,490
With this, I can win!

158
00:14:48,930 --> 00:14:51,740
Come at me with the power of a dragon!

159
00:14:52,760 --> 00:14:54,370
Here I come!

160
00:15:03,380 --> 00:15:06,590
I made it... The third lacrima...

161
00:15:06,590 --> 00:15:09,540
Lucy, hang in there...

162
00:15:10,550 --> 00:15:13,190
I knew it wasn't the time to show off,

163
00:15:14,060 --> 00:15:16,720
but I wasn't able to say I couldn't do it!

164
00:15:17,700 --> 00:15:19,170
Lucy?

165
00:15:19,170 --> 00:15:22,480
I'm completely out of magic power.

166
00:15:25,010 --> 00:15:28,440
Even so, I want to protect Wendy's guild!

167
00:15:28,820 --> 00:15:30,720
I don't want to get down on myself!

168
00:15:31,760 --> 00:15:35,300
That's why I'm going to keep 
going, until the bitter end!

169
00:15:38,940 --> 00:15:40,130
Lucy!

170
00:15:40,130 --> 00:15:43,170
I can't fall! Not in a place like this!

171
00:15:46,900 --> 00:15:48,090
Wendy...

172
00:15:48,900 --> 00:15:50,400
I have to do my best.

173
00:15:51,450 --> 00:15:53,400
For Caitshelter...

174
00:15:54,100 --> 00:15:57,010
For Jellal, who believed in me...

175
00:15:58,400 --> 00:16:01,480
And for all my other friends, too!

176
00:16:07,610 --> 00:16:10,750
Dark Gravity!

177
00:16:18,620 --> 00:16:21,930
Come on now... You can do better than that.

178
00:16:28,970 --> 00:16:30,130
Natsu...

179
00:16:35,880 --> 00:16:37,160
That was close...

180
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:52,320
Zero Slash!

181
00:17:17,560 --> 00:17:19,340
Dark Delete!

182
00:17:45,900 --> 00:17:50,500
No... I can't pass out yet!

183
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:54,380
Hibiki, Ren, Eve...

184
00:17:54,380 --> 00:17:57,220
Give me the power!

185
00:18:21,910 --> 00:18:23,330
3 more minutes.

186
00:18:28,660 --> 00:18:29,560
Natsu.

187
00:18:34,990 --> 00:18:38,220
Is that all there is to 
the power of a dragon?

188
00:18:38,550 --> 00:18:43,930
Dragons ruled in ancient times 
with this paltry amount of power?!

189
00:18:48,970 --> 00:18:51,560
W-What are you going to do, Lucy?

190
00:18:51,560 --> 00:18:53,150
I don't know!

191
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:57,570
I don't know, but maybe if 
I throw myself against it...

192
00:18:57,570 --> 00:18:59,720
I have to destroy it!

193
00:19:01,020 --> 00:19:05,380
I won't give up! I won't 
give, up no matter what!

194
00:19:06,050 --> 00:19:09,660
Sometimes, it's that feeling 
that can give you the power.

195
00:19:13,050 --> 00:19:15,190
We were listening back then.

196
00:19:15,190 --> 00:19:17,880
We heard your feelings.

197
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:19,320
Gemini...

198
00:19:20,350 --> 00:19:22,730
Why are you here?

199
00:19:26,230 --> 00:19:30,110
We can copy your body and abilities.

200
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:33,520
We'll become your will!

201
00:19:37,240 --> 00:19:40,140
We just need to destroy this thing 
in about three minutes, right?

202
00:19:40,140 --> 00:19:41,370
Thank you!

203
00:19:42,030 --> 00:19:44,130
Men... Men...

204
00:19:44,130 --> 00:19:48,880
I will show you my power parfum!

205
00:20:00,840 --> 00:20:05,240
More power... The power of the heavens...

206
00:20:08,950 --> 00:20:12,130
I am the master of Oracion Seis, Zero!

207
00:20:12,360 --> 00:20:16,240
I'm on a whole other level than a 
mere foot soldier from some guild.

208
00:20:21,450 --> 00:20:26,280
There's no way trash like 
you could handle me alone!

209
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:33,980
I'm not alone.

210
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:36,920
I can hear them...

211
00:20:38,820 --> 00:20:42,510
I can... hear them...

212
00:20:42,820 --> 00:20:47,430
I can hear everyone's voices... I 
can sense everyone's feelings...

213
00:20:47,860 --> 00:20:51,770
I'm not alone... Everyone's feelings...

214
00:20:52,390 --> 00:20:58,310
They support me... They are what 
give me the will to stand and fight.

215
00:21:09,230 --> 00:21:11,080
Guess it's about time.

216
00:21:14,020 --> 00:21:15,990
Okay, here we go!

217
00:21:15,990 --> 00:21:17,680
The Gate of the Golden Bull is good, right?

218
00:21:17,680 --> 00:21:19,390
Yes, please!

219
00:21:19,800 --> 00:21:26,580
Now is the time to show everyone the 
true power of Ichiya, of Blue Pegasus!

220
00:21:26,580 --> 00:21:27,510
Requip!

221
00:21:34,090 --> 00:21:38,190
Power... Power is welling 
up from within me...

222
00:21:38,700 --> 00:21:39,960
Wendy...

223
00:21:41,940 --> 00:21:48,910
The power... The power of my 
friends flows throughout my body!

224
00:21:49,360 --> 00:21:54,290
Dragon Force... It will be a shame 
to crush it to smithereens, but...

225
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:56,450
Enough.

226
00:21:57,060 --> 00:21:58,370
It's been fun.

227
00:21:58,880 --> 00:22:02,130
I will give you true nothingness.

228
00:22:02,400 --> 00:22:05,000
My greatest magic...

229
00:22:05,570 --> 00:22:07,920
Secret Dragon Slayer Art:

230
00:22:07,920 --> 00:22:10,310
Blazing Explosive Flame Edge!

231
00:22:10,310 --> 00:22:11,890
Genesis Zero!

232
00:22:14,330 --> 00:22:17,770
Vanish into the great nothingness!

233
00:23:56,900 --> 00:23:59,790
I wonder if there's a dragon walking around 
somewhere, that's just fallen through the cracks...

234
00:23:59,790 --> 00:24:02,000
Like a dragon would fall through a crack!

235
00:24:02,000 --> 00:24:06,500
If I had a dragon, I'd be able to train with 
my Dragon Slayer Magic whenever I wanted!

236
00:24:07,270 --> 00:24:11,260
Natsu! What do you want with 
a dragon when you have me?

237
00:24:11,260 --> 00:24:13,470
Why do you look like you 
just said something cool?

238
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:16,510
Next time: I'm with you!

239
00:24:16,760 --> 00:24:18,490
I mean, there's no way you could do it!

240
00:24:18,490 --> 00:24:22,460
If I feel like it, I can go 
toe-to-toe with any dragon!

241
00:24:22,790 --> 00:24:24,770
More like, toe-to-head.

